    <ul>
      <li><a href="/blog/regex-cheat-sheet">Regex Cheat Sheet for Developers</a> — syntax reference with code examples in JS and Python</li>
      <li><a href="/blog/common-regex-patterns">Common Regex Patterns: 20+ Examples</a> — production-ready patterns for emails, URLs, dates, and more</li>
